txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Sticky filth from the spiders north and east of Esteldín. Deliver the items to Ferrif within Esteldín.
'This will be used in a manner to help our people, thank you.'
'Like the filth from the spiders to the west, there are uses for this substance. Gather some for me, please.'
Rangers of Esteldín Task: Sticky Filth
Ferrif, a Ranger, has asked for a collection of sticky filth to be delivered to him at the Ranger's home at Esteldín.
Deliver the sticky filth to Ferrif in Esteldín
You have accepted a task to collect sticky filth from the spiders in the area surrounding Esteldín to the north and east. Once collected, you are to deliver the items to Ferrif within Esteldín.
Wanted: Sticky filth from the spiders north and east of Esteldín.
